OL,4,Cthreatening to kill JK Rowling with 'a
OL,5,Cbig hammer'
OL,7,FA man who posted "chilling" messages
OL,8,Fonline threatening to kill Harry
OL,9,FPotter author JK Rowling and former-MP
OL,10,FRosie Duffield has been sentenced.
OL,12,FGlenn Mullen, from , admitted to
OL,13,Fuploading voice recordings in Gaelic
OL,14,Fin which he threatened to kill JK
OL,15,FRowling "with a big hammer" and said
OL,16,Fhe would "see Rosie Duffield at the
OL,17,Fbar with a big gun", Westminster
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court heard on Tuesday.
