OL,7,FMullen, 31, had posted the threat in
OL,8,FJanuary 2023 on X, then known as
OL,9,FTwitter, and was eventually identified
OL,10,Fpublicly by an online magazine.
OL,12,FThe court heard how Scottish author JK
OL,13,FRowling felt the threats were "quite
OL,14,Fchilling" and "appeared calculating".
OL,16,FThe prosecution added: "They made her
OL,17,Flook over her shoulder and worry about
OL,18,Fthe safety of her family and her
OL,19,Fchildren."
