OL,7,FThe court heard the messages made
OL,8,FRosie Duffield, who is the Labour
OL,9,FGeneral Election candidate in
OL,10,FCanterbury, feel "nervous walking
OL,11,Faround her constituency, where she was
OL,12,Fvisible and easily accessible".
OL,14,FDuring a police interview on 10 March
OL,15,F2023, Mullen gave no comment to
OL,16,Fpolice. However, he went on to make
OL,17,F"full and frank admissions" to making
OL,18,Fthe threats at a later interview on 6
OL,19,FOctober.
