OL,7,FHanding down two suspended sentences,
OL,8,Fchief magistrate Paul Goldspring said
OL,9,FMullen's actions were part of a
OL,10,F"modern phenomena" of people on social
OL,11,Fmedia sites "hiding behind a keyboard
OL,12,Fto threaten, abuse or harass people in
OL,13,Fthe public eye".
OL,15,FMr Goldspring handed down two eight-
OL,16,Fweek prison sentences, suspended for
OL,17,Ftwo years, to be served concurrently.
