OL,7,FHe also ordered Mullen to complete a
OL,8,F12-month community order, including 20
OL,9,Fdays rehabilitation activity
OL,10,Frequirement and 150 hours of unpaid
OL,11,Fwork.
OL,13,FHe said: "There seems to be this
OL,14,Fmodern phenomena that Twitter and
OL,15,Fother social media and online
OL,16,Fplatforms allow you to say and do what
OL,17,Fyou like ` and particularly people in
OL,18,Fthe public eye, lots of people think
OL,19,Fare fair game.
