OL,7,FIn a statement after the sentencing,
OL,8,FCPS senior crown prosecutor John Moran
OL,9,Fsaid: "The messages uploaded to social
OL,10,Fmedia were targeted and very
OL,11,Fconcerning.
OL,13,F"The audio clips have had a
OL,14,Fsignificant impact on the two victims,
OL,15,Fwho described feeling upset, worried
OL,16,Fand distressed when they heard them.
OL,18,F"Nobody has the right to issue threats
OL,19,For abuse, whether that be in person or
OL,20,Fvia social media."
